=Ojibwe=
==ᔒᐦᔒ (''zhiishii'')==
===Definitions===
# (miscellaneous): reduplication form of ᔒ (''zhii'')

===Other Roman orthographies===
* Algonquin: ''jîcî''
** Cuoq: ''cici''
* Ontario Saulteaux: ''shiihshii''
* Manitoba Saulteaux: ''šīhšī''
* Baraga: ''jishi''

==ᔒᐦᔒᐝ (''zhiishii'')==
===Etmology===
< {{PA.}} *''šīʔšīy'' (gourd/rattle)

===Definitions===
# (v): non-existing verb-root common to all Ojibwe words that indicate rattling.
#* derived words:
#** ᔒᐦᔒᐝᑯ (''[[zhiishiigo]]'')
#** ᔒᐦᔒᐝᑴ (''[[zhiishiigwe]]'')
#** ᔒᐦᔒᐝᑾᓐ (''[[zhiishiigwan]]'')
#** ᔒᐦᔒᐝᑾᓇᓐ (''[[zhiishiigwanan]]'')

===Other Roman orthographies===
* Algonquin: ''jîcî''
** Cuoq: ''cici'' (087c)
* Ontario Saulteaux: ''shiihshii''
* Manitoba Saulteaux: ''šīhšī''
* Baraga: ''jishi''

